making most mistakes in the RPG this week*  Then Spears was dreaming 
she was in a room that collapsed.  She is in the CF safe and sound.

::Spears::

She was still in her dream that she was trapped under the rubbled of 
the ship.  Her trainer program was still working on the device that 
kept her in stasis lock.  She moanded in her sleep,"noo,  heellpp."
as she moved and squirmed under the straps.  A thin ribbon of smoke 
escaped from where the device was attached on her.
